title.narrative: Private Sector Renewable Energy and Energy Efficiency Project

description.narrative: The Project's development objective is to help increase privately owned and operated energy production from indigenous renewable sources within the market-based framework of the Turkish Electricity Market Law, enhance demand-side energy efficiency, and thereby help reduce greenhouse gas emissions.
